name: 5 Elegant Bridesmaids Cards
description:
These are unique Elegant Themed "will you be my bridesmaid cards". A great way to ask that special person to be in your wedding party. 

These Bridesmaids cards go with the following Invitation Collection: Brooke, Rachel and Marlo.

These were created upon the customer's request to have each card personalized for each girl with her name and a special message for just her. We also did them in the girls colors in which they would be wearing in the wedding. 

Price: 
$27.50 for 5 or $5.50 each to add more

Card: Z-Card with personalized panels in Peal with Tiffany Blue ribbon to hold card closed along with one White envelope.

We are also always willing to create new designs base on your request. Brides Maid Card can be created using any of our design graphics posted or custom. Please contact studio.
